data.text:
Fabio Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Fabio is recorded 283,252 times globally, ranking it as the 126th most common name worldwide.

Fabio is most prevalent in Italy, with 213,157 occurrences, making it the 19th most popular name in the country.
